  <description><![CDATA[<p>Enjoying one of the best locations in the valley, the Christiania offers high levels of service in an inviting setting. Ski in/out position and just 100m from the Piz La Ila gondola. With comfortable and stylish bars/lounge that are perfect for relaxing and taking in the stunning scenery of the Dolomites. The extensive wellness area boasts 3 saunas, steam room, sensory showers, kneipp, gym and indoor pool with panoramic views (free). Massages and beauty treatments available (pay locally).</p>
<p><strong>Hotel Christiania is bookable on request only. Please call to enquire.</strong></p>]]></description>
